{
  "chapter": 46,
  "chapter_summary": "唐迪纵火烧马企图杀害展梦白与萧飞雨，火势蔓延成灾。蓝大先生、铁驼、烈火夫人等高手赶来救火，铁驼从火中救出唐凤。蓝大先生与烈火夫人为唐凤治伤，苏浅雪出现，趁机将唐凤带走，实与唐迪暗中勾结。展梦白与萧飞雨以金蝉脱壳之计逃脱，骑马逃入荒山。两人在溪边短暂温存后，展梦白坚持前往洞庭君山探查真相。夜行途中遭遇唐迪设伏，唐门暗器封喉杀马，两人身陷绝境。关键时刻，唐门老祖宗唐无影乘软轿出现，厉声斥责唐迪，打灭灯火救下展梦白与萧飞雨。唐无影对展梦白透露的\"盒子\"与\"君山\"之事似有所知，却讳莫如深，暗示二人前往君山自行探寻。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_di",
      "speaker_name": "唐迪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "宁可射死马，莫要放走了人。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_di",
      "speaker_name": "唐迪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在那里。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_di",
      "speaker_name": "唐迪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "展梦白呀展梦白，你莫怪老夫心狠手辛，谁要你多管闲事？谁要你探听老夫的秘密。",
      "tone": "徒得",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_di",
      "speaker_name": "唐迪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "烧死最好……烧死最好……",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_di",
      "speaker_name": "唐迪",
      "listener": "char_su_qian_xue",
      "text": "死了。",
      "tone": "陌然",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_qian_xue",
      "speaker_name": "苏浅雪",
      "listener": "char_tang_di",
      "text": "什么死了？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_di",
      "speaker_name": "唐迪",
      "listener": "char_su_qian_xue",
      "text": "三个人都死了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_qian_xue",
      "speaker_name": "苏浅雪",
      "listener": "char_tang_di",
      "text": "死了也好。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_bao",
      "speaker_name": "唐豹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这究竟是怎么回事？究竟是如何起的火？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_men_di_zi",
      "speaker_name": "唐门子弟",
      "listener": "char_tang_bao",
      "text": "小的也不知道，只是老爷……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_bao",
      "speaker_name": "唐豹",
      "listener": "char_tang_men_di_zi",
      "text": "老爷在哪里？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_bao",
      "speaker_name": "唐豹",
      "listener": "char_tang_di",
      "text": "爹爹方才哪里去了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_di",
      "speaker_name": "唐迪",
      "listener": "char_tang_bao",
      "text": "为父始终在这里，正要问你哪里去了？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_bao",
      "speaker_name": "唐豹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "莫非我眼睛了么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你我不必打了，谁救熄这火，才算是真英雄。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_di",
      "speaker_name": "唐迪",
      "listener": "char_tang_bao",
      "text": "豹儿，咱们过去看看，是什么人来了？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_tuo",
      "speaker_name": "铁验",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "奇怪，这里还有个人。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": "char_tie_tuo",
      "text": "烤熟了没有？",
      "tone": "调催",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_tuo",
      "speaker_name": "铁验",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "奇怪，这人还未死。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_di",
      "speaker_name": "唐迪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是哪位前辈高手，唐迪在这里。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_di",
      "speaker_name": "唐迪",
      "listener": "char_tie_tuo",
      "text": "多谢前辈相救……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_tuo",
      "speaker_name": "铁验",
      "listener": "char_tang_di",
      "text": "你抱着。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 127
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "火灭了有何不好？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_tuo",
      "speaker_name": "铁验",
      "listener": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "text": "这是你三人救灭的火，你三人才是英雄？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": "char_tie_tuo",
      "text": "好个好胜的老儿，你莫非不知救人更胜过救火。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_tuo",
      "speaker_name": "铁验",
      "listener": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "text": "这还像话……你我四人还是该继续打上一架。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": "char_tie_tuo",
      "text": "只可惜这架已打不成了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": "char_tang_di",
      "text": "这位姓娘是什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_di",
      "speaker_name": "唐迪",
      "listener": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "text": "正是小女，在下唐迪，不知两位前辈大名？",
      "tone": "恩勤",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_tuo",
      "speaker_name": "铁验",
      "listener": "char_tang_di",
      "text": "我两人的姓名，你不必问了，且放下你女儿。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_di",
      "speaker_name": "唐迪",
      "listener": "char_tie_tuo",
      "text": "区区小事，不敢惊动前辈。",
      "tone": "恩勤",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_tuo",
      "speaker_name": "铁验",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "吴七、杨飞，你两人若是有种，就回来与老子再打一架，走了的不算英雄。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_di",
      "speaker_name": "唐迪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这人既不将女儿交给自己儿子，反要外人抱着，这件事俱都不合情理。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lie_huo_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "烈火夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小蓝，我找得你好苦……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哎呀，不好！她来了……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_tuo",
      "speaker_name": "铁验",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么人来了？你怕……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lie_huo_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "烈火夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_tuo",
      "text": "好呀，你这验子打跑了小蓝，我找你算账。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_tuo",
      "speaker_name": "铁验",
      "listener": "char_lie_huo_fu_ren",
      "text": "我可打不跑他，是你骇走他的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 199
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lie_huo_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "烈火夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_tuo",
      "text": "你这验子说什么？我又不是母夜叉，他骇个什么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我在这里，你来吧！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lie_huo_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "烈火夫人",
      "listener": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "text": "小蓝，是你么？你要找我，你就快过来，为何要我过去？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这里有个被火烧伤的人，要你来救。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 227
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lie_huo_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "烈火夫人",
      "listener": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "text": "原来是有事求着我了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_tuo",
      "speaker_name": "铁验",
      "listener": "char_lie_huo_fu_ren",
      "text": "姓奶奶，人家求你，你就快去吧！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lie_huo_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "烈火夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_tuo",
      "text": "便宜你这验子了。",
      "tone": "调催",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lie_huo_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "烈火夫人",
      "listener": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "text": "小蓝，你抱的是谁？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": "char_lie_huo_fu_ren",
      "text": "她受了火伤，昏迷不醒……",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lie_huo_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "烈火夫人",
      "listener": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "text": "好呀，你巴巴唤我来，只是为她治伤，这小妖精是什么人？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": "char_lie_huo_fu_ren",
      "text": "唉！七老八十了，还要吃醋。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lie_huo_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "烈火夫人",
      "listener": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "text": "好，我老了，她年轻，我走就是。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": "char_lie_huo_fu_ren",
      "text": "唉！你定要走，我也无法。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lie_huo_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "烈火夫人",
      "listener": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "text": "我偏偏不走，也不替她治伤，看你怎么？",
      "tone": "调催",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 257
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": "char_lie_huo_fu_ren",
      "text": "你良心最好，救火伤的本事，天下更是只有烈火夫人最妙。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 261
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lie_huo_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "烈火夫人",
      "listener": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "text": "谁要你拍马屁，但你一拍马屁，我心又软了，救就救吧。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": "char_lie_huo_fu_ren",
      "text": "我做她爷爷都嫌老了，还会怎样？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_di",
      "speaker_name": "唐迪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不知前辈要……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": "char_tang_di",
      "text": "你要怎样？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_di",
      "speaker_name": "唐迪",
      "listener": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "text": "在下只是不敢劳动……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": "char_tang_di",
      "text": "站开一边，莫要多话。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lie_huo_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "烈火夫人",
      "listener": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "text": "小蓝，咱们好久未见，也该找个地方聊聊去了，我陪你喝两杯。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 323
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_da_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "蓝大先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是，我正想喝两杯。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_di",
      "speaker_name": "唐迪",
      "listener": "char_su_qian_xue",
      "text": "小女已被家爷逐出了门墙。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_qian_xue",
      "speaker_name": "苏浅雪",
      "listener": "char_tang_di",
      "text": "既是如此，唐大侠不如将令嫓交托给我，带回治伤。",
      "tone": "恩勤",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 349
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_di",
      "speaker_name": "唐迪",
      "listener": "char_su_qian_xue",
      "text": "固所愿也，不敢请矣。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_qian_xue",
      "speaker_name": "苏浅雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哎呀，唐姐姐受了伤，姐姐，你治得好么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lie_huo_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "烈火夫人",
      "listener": "char_su_qian_xue",
      "text": "烧得很厉害，一时还真难治好。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_qian_xue",
      "speaker_name": "苏浅雪",
      "listener": "char_lie_huo_fu_ren",
      "text": "你是个忙人，不如让我来吧。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 301
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lie_huo_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "烈火夫人",
      "listener": "char_su_qian_xue",
      "text": "谁不知道你是个女才子、万事通、机灵鬼，有你出手，是她的福气。",
      "tone": "调催",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 305
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_qian_xue",
      "speaker_name": "苏浅雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你看，一下子给了我三个外号……轻续，快把唐姐姐抱走。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_qian_xue",
      "speaker_name": "苏浅雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你把她抱走，咱们都该走了，别熬人家的风景。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 313
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_di",
      "speaker_name": "唐迪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只有一件衣衫？那两人到哪里去了？……哎呀，老夫竟中了他们金蝉脱壳之计。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_di",
      "speaker_name": "唐迪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "下令搜索，只见着展梦白、萫飞雨两人，只管以最毒的暗器下手，快，快去！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 377
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萫飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "驯儿你莫怪我，你救了咱们出来，我反而伤了你。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萫飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你几时醒的？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 423
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "没有多久。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萫飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你还渴么？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "我忘了渴不渴。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萫飞雨",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "要是爷爷在这里就好了……又不知那位唐姐姐此刻怎样了？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "洞庭君山。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萫飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "但……但你的伤……",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "夜深行路……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萫飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "夜深行路的，也未必是坏人，我肚子实在饿了。",
      "tone": "调催",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 467
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不好，是唐家的人，咱们快走。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萫飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你这人真糊涂，唐家的人又不知道地道中的人就是咱们。",
      "tone": "调催",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "但如此深夜，他们为何在荒山走动？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萫飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "说不定是出来送客的，灯笼上又怎会写明唐字。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 483
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "这倒不错。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "对方稍有异动，立行打马！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 508,
      "line_end": 508
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "来的可是唐门朋友么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 510
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "走。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 514
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萫飞雨",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "闯！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 520,
      "line_end": 520
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "闯不得。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 524,
      "line_end": 524
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_di",
      "speaker_name": "唐迪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "姓展的果然还有些光头，你两人要再动一动，便先尝尝一步封喉，五毒神砂的滋味！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 526,
      "line_end": 527
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你虽故意改变语声，但我已知道你是什么人了，唐门暗器，果然狠毒。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 534
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_di",
      "speaker_name": "唐迪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你知道就好。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 538,
      "line_end": 538
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你要怎样？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 540,
      "line_end": 540
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萫飞雨",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们杀了我，放了他吧，他什么都不知道。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 548,
      "line_end": 548
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "胡说，我的伤反正已……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 552,
      "line_end": 552
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_di",
      "speaker_name": "唐迪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "妙极妙极，原来你已受伤。",
      "tone": "徒得",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 556,
      "line_end": 556
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_di",
      "speaker_name": "唐迪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "莫放这两人走了，我去看看！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 576,
      "line_end": 576
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_di",
      "speaker_name": "唐迪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "孩儿迎驾。",
      "tone": "敬畏",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 586,
      "line_end": 587
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_wu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "唐无影",
      "listener": "char_tang_di",
      "text": "起来吧！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 596,
      "line_end": 596
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_wu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "唐无影",
      "listener": "char_tang_di",
      "text": "你还认得我这爷爷么？唐迪，唐大侠！你做了这些轰轰烈烈的事，我这残废老人何曾知道。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 598,
      "line_end": 600
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_di",
      "speaker_name": "唐迪",
      "listener": "char_tang_wu_ying",
      "text": "孩儿不敢……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 602,
      "line_end": 602
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_wu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "唐无影",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "改过！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 608,
      "line_end": 608
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_wu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "唐无影",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "别的我不管，展梦白犯了什么过错，你定要杀他？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 616,
      "line_end": 617
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_di",
      "speaker_name": "唐迪",
      "listener": "char_tang_wu_ying",
      "text": "孩儿只当他是故意来此卧底的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 620,
      "line_end": 620
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_wu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "唐无影",
      "listener": "char_tang_di",
      "text": "混账，住口！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 622,
      "line_end": 622
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_wu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "唐无影",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "展梦白，你过来，我且问你，你到底是听到他的什么秘密？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 628,
      "line_end": 630
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_tang_wu_ying",
      "text": "晚辋只得他要将一个盒子送至君山。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 632,
      "line_end": 632
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_wu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "唐无影",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "盒子？……君山？……好……好……好……好……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 634,
      "line_end": 634
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_wu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "唐无影",
      "listener": "char_tang_di",
      "text": "唐迪，还不快带着你这些狐群狗党先回去，静候发落。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 636,
      "line_end": 637
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_wu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "唐无影",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大事夫难免妻不贤子不孝，我怎的会有你这种儿子。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 642,
      "line_end": 643
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萫飞雨",
      "listener": "char_tang_wu_ying",
      "text": "盒子里究竟有什么秘密？你老人家莫非知道么？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 646,
      "line_end": 647
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_wu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "唐无影",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "要等问过方知。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 650,
      "line_end": 650
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "speaker_name": "萫飞雨",
      "listener": "char_tang_wu_ying",
      "text": "君山里有何秘密，你老人家必定是知道的了。",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 652,
      "line_end": 653
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_wu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "唐无影",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fei_yu",
      "text": "你要知君山的秘密，为何不到君山去看看？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 656,
      "line_end": 657
    }
  ],
